Weak Force ($\alpha_2$): Your v8w run just showed it evolves from $\approx 0.034$ (at $M_Z$) to $\approx 0.021$ at $10^{17}$ GeV.

The Conclusion:

$\alpha_s(Q_0) \approx \alpha_2(Q_0) \approx 0.02$.

